1. **Multiple interpretability examples across diverse complex types**: One visualization (PDB ID: 4kz6) cannot establish interpretability. The paper should show attention visualizations for 5-10 diverse complexes (different protein classes, binding modes, affinity ranges) with comparison to known binding sites.

